{"tid":1554910,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友哋喺台灣幫香港求到枝好籤","createTime":"2019-09-09T07:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T07:08:15.000Z","uid":80881,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8ab35127f2cd8dfe3aceb8061bfe8a2b4c9cfce9","tid":1554910,"uid":80881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:07:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FYeRg4H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFYeRg4H.jpg&h=48671d74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n籤詩是人生方向的指引，是你命運的明燈，抓住籤詩的玄機，與菩薩給你的忠告，以讓你生命走向更順遂與喜悅......本閣籤詩有完整的籤詩故事，與精要解籤，讓你把握籤詩的精華，與抓住改造命運的重心。<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好放棄！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"1d60ce7af977af81916c6e577c449e8d7520db32","tid":1554910,"uid":80881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:08:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://fortune-poems.blogspot.com/2013/09/48_11.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffortune-poems.blogspot.com%2F2013%2F09%2F48_11.html&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kZq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=f7543a53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fortune-poems.blogspot.com/2013/09/48_11.html</a><br />\n<br />\n詳細籤解"}]}